00:27:53,900 --> 00:27:54,740
You liar!

546
00:27:54,780 --> 00:27:55,660
I'm sorry.

547
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:57,340
I'm sorry, Xiaoying.

548
00:27:57,360 --> 00:27:58,860
