00:28:18,900 --> 00:28:20,990
♪I am gifted in this aspect♪

562
00:28:21,160 --> 00:28:23,360
♪You and I walking side by side♪

563
00:28:23,650 --> 00:28:25,940
♪I say all the truth in reverse♪

564
00:28:25,940 --> 00:28:27,620
