566
00:28:31,620 --> 00:28:32,520
Xiaoying,

567
00:28:34,900 --> 00:28:36,420
please don't be sad.

568
00:28:37,620 --> 00:28:39,300
Now that Xiaolu is back,

569
00:28:39,700 --> 00:28:40,860
